<section class="item">
<a href="//www.pingwest.com/a/299267" target="_blank" class="title">10月30日，北京，一起感受 AI for Real</a>
<p class="author">
<a href="//www.pingwest.com/user/74474943" target="_blank" class="name">PRO</a>
